Interface Schedules

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.vmware.vapi.internal.bindings.CompletionStageService, SchedulesTypes, Service
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SchedulesStub

    public interface Schedules
extends Service, SchedulesTypes, com.vmware.vapi.internal.bindings.CompletionStageService
    The Schedules interface provides methods to be performed to manage backup schedules. This interface was added in vSphere API 6.7.
